---
import Container from '../shared/Container.astro';
---

<section class="py-12" style="background: var(--bg-card)">
  <Container size="wide">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-6 justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">🎙️</span>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: var(--text)">透透气</h2>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color: var(--c-workshop); border-color: var(--c-workshop)">播客</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary)">
          那些「本该如此」的东西，重新看一眼。与小瑶坊合作的独立播客项目。
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/podcast/"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border transition-all hover:opacity-80"
        style="color: var(--text); border-color: var(--border-strong)"
      >
        了解更多 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
